Packages/*/

# ===========================
# TRACKED (for clarity)
# ===========================
# .gitignore
# Assets/_GRIMMORPG/    -- all GRPG code, art, audio, data, prefabs, scenes, UI
# Documents/            -- GDD, status, dev reference
# ProjectSettings/      -- Unity project configuration
# Packages/manifest.json + packages-lock.json
